
##### installer.sh #####

awsinstall.sh - Installs for an Amazon Linux image

linuxinstall.sh - Installs for any Linux

Run as:
sudo sh ramaddainstaller/awsinstall.sh
or:
sudo sh ramaddainstaller/linuxinstall.sh 


This will walk you through a number of installation steps to setup the directories, and,
on Amazon Linux, install and configure Postgres


##
## Service
##
On Amazon Linux to start/stop RAMADDA:
sudo sh service ramadda stop
sudo sh service ramadda start


##
## Updating
##

To update your install run:

On Amazon Linux:
sudo sh ramaddainstaller/awsupdate.sh

or in Linux:
sudo sh ramaddainstaller/linuxupdate.sh

